data.description: Nestled in a desirable neighborhood served by Cullman City Schools, this 2022-built gem offers a modern haven for family living. Spanning 2,033 sq ft, this 3 bed, 2.5 bath home delights with an open floor plan graced by tray ceilings featuring tongue & groove accents in both the living room and master suite. The gourmet kitchen, boasting quartz countertops and Venetian gold finishes, invites you to unleash your culinary skills. The split floor plan ensures privacy for the luxurious master suite, which includes a large soaking tub, a glass-enclosed shower, double vanities, and a spacious walk-in closet. Outside, the fenced backyard and covered porch provide a serene retreat. This is a turn-key home ready to create new memories.
